@startuml SAFE-AI Excel梳理小工具 Use Case Diagram

' ============================================
' SAFE-AI Excel 梳理小工具 — Use Case Diagram
' ============================================

left to right direction
skinparam actorStyle awesome
skinparam packageStyle rectangle
skinparam usecase {
  BackgroundColor #F6F7F9
  BorderColor #1a1f2e
  ArrowColor #2b6cb0
}
skinparam actor {
  BackgroundColor #ebf3fb
  BorderColor #2b6cb0
}

' --- Actors ---
actor "傳統產業\n資料擁有者" as Owner #ebf3fb
actor "AI 導入顧問\n/ 系統整合商" as Consultant #e6f4f1
actor "系統管理者" as Admin #fdf3e7

' --- External Systems ---
actor "Gemini API" as Gemini <<外部系統>>
actor "區塊鏈服務" as Blockchain <<外部系統>>

' --- System Boundary ---
rectangle "SAFE-AI Excel 梳理小工具" {

  package "帳號管理" {
    usecase "註冊帳號" as UC1
    usecase "登入系統" as UC2
    usecase "登出系統" as UC3
  }

  package "資料上傳與評估" {
    usecase "上傳 Excel / CSV" as UC4
    usecase "選擇 Sheet" as UC5
    usecase "執行 AI Data\nReadiness 評估" as UC6
    usecase "查看評估報告\n（六項指標 + 總分）" as UC7
    usecase "查看問題清單\n（嚴重度 + 建議）" as UC8
  }

  package "分流與梳理" {
    usecase "選擇處理路徑\n（梳理 / 重新上傳）" as UC9
    usecase "套用批次規則\n（日期/重複/名稱/小計）" as UC11
    usecase "逐列處理\n（填 N/A / 刪除）" as UC12
    usecase "補齊後重新上傳" as UC13
  }

  package "產出與存證" {
    usecase "下載 refined.xlsx" as UC14
    usecase "下載 PDF 報告\n（美觀排版）" as UC15
    usecase "下載 cleaning.log" as UC16
    usecase "提交 Evidence 存證\n（SHA-256 hash）" as UC17
    usecase "查驗存證狀態" as UC18
  }

  package "前後對比問答" {
    usecase "提出資料問題" as UC19
    usecase "查看前後對比回答\n（左右並排）" as UC20
    usecase "使用建議問題" as UC21
    usecase "同意資料保護聲明" as UC22
  }

  package "系統設定" {
    usecase "調整評分權重\n（六項指標滑桿）" as UC23
  }
}

' --- Owner relationships ---
Owner --> UC1
Owner --> UC2
Owner --> UC3
Owner --> UC4
Owner --> UC6
Owner --> UC7
Owner --> UC8
Owner --> UC9
Owner --> UC11
Owner --> UC12
Owner --> UC13
Owner --> UC14
Owner --> UC15
Owner --> UC16
Owner --> UC17
Owner --> UC18
Owner --> UC19
Owner --> UC20
Owner --> UC21

' --- Consultant relationships ---
Consultant --> UC2
Consultant --> UC4
Consultant --> UC6
Consultant --> UC7
Consultant --> UC15

' --- Admin relationships ---
Admin --> UC2
Admin --> UC23

' --- Include / Extend ---
UC4 ..> UC5 : <<include>>
UC6 ..> UC7 : <<include>>
UC6 ..> UC8 : <<include>>
UC19 ..> UC22 : <<include>>
UC19 ..> UC20 : <<include>>
UC9 ..> UC11 : <<extend>>\n選擇「以現況梳理」
UC9 ..> UC13 : <<extend>>\n選擇「補齊後重新上傳」

' --- External system relationships ---
UC19 --> Gemini
UC17 --> Blockchain
UC18 --> Blockchain

' --- Notes ---
note right of Owner
  **典型客戶畫像**
  ──────────────
  • 製造業、貿易業、零售業、物流業
  • 中小企業（50-500人）
  • 核心資料仍以 Excel 管理
  • 想導入 AI 但卡在「資料品質」
  • 沒有資料工程師
  • 需要簡單工具評估「我的資料
    離 AI 還有多遠」
  
  **典型資料**
  ──────────
  • 業績訂單報表
  • 庫存盤點表
  • BOM 物料清單
  • 稽核 / 檢查表
end note

note right of Consultant
  **顧問使用情境**
  ──────────────
  • 快速評估客戶資料品質
  • 產出 PDF 報告附在提案書中
  • 向客戶說明「哪些資料需先整理」
end note

note bottom of Gemini
  僅用於模組 F
  前後對比問答
  （非評估計算）
end note

note bottom of Blockchain
  本專案僅定義
  API 接口
  實作在另一個
  專案中
end note

@enduml
